Can you generate a compelling social media marketing tagline for C++ language? The provided code displays a simple example to help you kick start your creativity:
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;
int main() {
   cout << "C++: The language that speaks for itself. #CodeWithC++" << endl;
   return 0;
}
Your task is to come up with an innovative and catchy slogan, which can go viral on various social media platforms. Please make sure to consider the unique features of C++ and craft a slogan that explicitly highlights them. Additionally, your slogan should be capable of appealing to a diverse range of audience segments.
